lead_paragraph: Carlos Rivas tied it in the 90th minute and Orlando City survived New England's late chances in a 2-2 tie with the Revolution on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Rivas' Late Goal Gives Orlando City 2-2 Draw With Revolution
